Cyber Claw:





Cyber Claw didn't like Hell Beast one bit. He reminded her of Megatron all 
too much. She shrank back, with her instincts kicking at her, telling her to 
run, telling her to fight. He growl developed in her throat. Her jagged 
teeth bared along with the display.

"I am Cyber Claw," she said, in a not so confident tone. "I came here to 
hear of Megatron's whereabouts. "I want to kill the son of a maintenance 
bot."
